description: Number of rooted unlabeled strongly connected digraphs with n nodes.
comments: There is a rather difficult formula (simplified in 1973). The subsequent published value 6222928 for n=6 needs to be verified.
references: V. A. Liskovets, The number of strongly connected directed graphs, Mat. Notes, 8 (1970), 877-882.
author: _Valery A. Liskovets_
